thread.title: A-1 Fence Company Wins Milwaukee Journal Sentinel Top Choice Award
thread.title_full: A-1 Fence Company Wins Milwaukee Journal Sentinel Top Choice Award

author: Brent Crubaugh
title: A-1 Fence Company Wins Milwaukee Journal Sentinel Top Choice Award
text:
The readers of The Milwaukee Journal Sentinel voted A-1 Fence the best fence company in Milwaukee in its inaugural Top Choice Awards. The awards were announced in August. You can view A-1 Fence and all of the Top Choice Award Winners at jsonline.com/topchoice . The Top Choice Awards honor outstanding businesses in the Milwaukee metro area. Readers vote on the best businesses in 100 distinct categories.
“At A-1 Fence we strive to provide unsurpassed quality and customer service while offering the very best custom fences, gazebos, and pergolas. This award tells us we’re on the right track,” says the owner and president, Dave Dezutel. “We’re extremely thankful to our customers for voting us the #1 fence contractor in the greater Milwaukee area.”
A-1 Fence has been serving the Milwaukee metro area since 1977. The company mills its own wood and has a reputation for building fences that look great and typically last longer than average due to the thicker wood that they mill. They were also the winner of an Angie’s List Super Service award in 2013. You can learn more about the company and their services by visiting http://www.a1-fence.com .
